data.text:
Kyle Korver - Points

Kyle Korver scores a career high 31 points (2006)

On February 24, 2006, Kyle Korver tied his career high in points in a NBA game. That day he scored 31 points in Philadelphia's road win against Milwaukee, 111-116. He also had 2 rebounds. He shot 6/10 from two, 4/7 from three, shooting at 58.8% from the field. He also shot 7/7 from the free-throw line.

Kyle Korver - Rebounds

Kyle Korver grabs a career high 13 rebounds (2003)

On March 01, 2003, Kyle Korver set his career high in rebounds in a NCAA game. That day he grabbed 13 rebounds in Creighton Bluejays's road loss against Southern Illinois Salukis, 70-62. He also had 10 points, 4 assists and 1 block.

Kyle Korver - Assists

Kyle Korver gives a career high 9 assists (2005)

On January 28, 2005, Kyle Korver tied his career high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 9 assists in Philadelphia's road loss against New Orleans, 99-95. He also had 16 points, 4 rebounds and 1 block.

Kyle Korver - Steals

Kyle Korver has a career high 6 steals (2005)

On March 04, 2005, Kyle Korver set his career high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 6 steals in Philadelphia's home win against Cleveland, 98-89. He also had 7 points, 6 rebounds and 4 assists.

Kyle Korver - Blocks

Kyle Korver blocks a career high 4 shots (2008)

On February 01, 2008, Kyle Korver tied his career high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 4 blocks in Utah's road win against Washington, 87-96. He also had 8 points, 2 rebounds and 4 assists.

Kyle Korver - Efficiency

Kyle Korver records a career high 38 efficiency rating (2015)

On November 06, 2015, Kyle Korver set his career high in efficiency in a NBA game. That day he accomplished 38 efficiency in Atlanta's road win against New Orleans, 115-121. He also had 22 points, 7 rebounds and 5 assists.
